token_info.name: Welcome to 0psib Land
token_info.description: Hello!!! Welcome to my little crazy world! This is an interactive little art I made with Construct 2! You can move the orc (also known as 'me, 0psib' - Yes, I'm a orc on real life) using the left and right arrow of you keyboard. I'm a new artist and this is a welcome and some informations about my art! I hope you like it! Thank you for the minutes you spent reading this =) Stay well, Stay safe! May the sun shine upon you.
